    "redesign_intro": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "disabled": true,
      "name": "Redesign intro",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"page-width page-width--narrow custom-liquid-redesign\" style=\"padding:1rem 0 2rem; text-align:left;\"><p style=\"font-size:1.6rem; line-height:1.7;\">A wedding band should feel like you — today. Whether yours is worn, dated, no longer fits, or you simply want something new while keeping its meaning, I can redesign, upgrade, or repurpose it — reusing your own gold and stones, or adding new ones I supply.</p><h2>Can you remake my wedding band?</h2><p>Yes. Remaking a wedding band is one of the most budget-friendly redesigns, because I refine and reuse your original gold and reset any stones into the new design.</p><h2>Why remake a wedding ring?</h2><p>Rings wear down, sizes change, and styles evolve. Remaking lets you keep the gold, the stones, and the meaning while creating a band you'll love wearing every day.</p><h2>Can you upgrade my wedding ring?</h2><p>Yes. I can upgrade your wedding ring by resetting it into a larger or higher-quality stone, adding diamonds, or moving to a more durable metal like platinum — using your own gold and stones, or new ones I supply. You keep the meaning and gain a ring that truly feels like an upgrade.</p><h2>Can you use my old gold to remake the band?</h2><p>Yes. I responsibly refine the gold you already have and apply its value toward the new band — preserving sentiment, lowering cost, and being kinder to the environment. <a href=\"/pages/use-your-own-gems-metal\">How using your own gold works →</a></p><h2>Can you repurpose my old wedding ring or gold?</h2><p>Absolutely. If you no longer wear a ring, I can repurpose its gold and stones into something new — another ring, a pendant, or a pair of earrings — so nothing meaningful sits unused in a drawer.</p><h2>Can two rings become one?</h2><p>Often, yes. I can combine an engagement ring and wedding band — or two inherited bands — into a single new piece. <a href=\"/pages/heirloom-jewelry-redesign\">Explore heirloom redesign →</a></p><h2>How much does it cost to remake a wedding band?</h2><p>It depends on the new design and metal weight, but reusing your own gold keeps it affordable. <a href=\"/pages/jewelry-redesign-cost\">See the pricing guide →</a></p><h2>How do I start?</h2><p>Book a free virtual consultation and send photos of your band. I'll design the new ring and give you a transparent quote before any work begins — entirely remotely if you prefer.</p><p style=\"margin-top:2.5rem;\"><a href=\"/pages/contact\" class=\"button\">Book your free consultation</a></p></div>",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 24,
        "padding_bottom": 12
      }
    },
